title: John Cena Moved to Tears By a Surprise Meeting with Fans | What's Trending Now!

json.text: WWE Superstar John Cena was surprised by a
group of fans and was moved to tears by their heartfelt fan letters. Welcome back
to What's Trending, I'm Shira Lazar. Be sure to LIKE this video and SUBSCRIBE
for more. Hidden camera video begins with John Cena reading a stack of fan letters.
And you can see that he's pretty touched by all these
incredible messages. I was even getting a little... But the climax of
this has to be when he watches one video message from a young fan.
Okay the tears are coming now. And little does Cena know, and we don't
want to add any spoilers here, but all the fans are waiting backstage to greet
him and surprise him.
One by one you see them greet their hero who is moved to
tears by their stories. Come on. It's okay to cry! Even a big, bulgy bro man like
John Cena cries! See? It's natural, it's human. We want to know what sort of feels does
this video give you? Let us know in the COMMENTS below now!
This hidden camera video is a follow up from a John Cena prank that he did on
his fans about a month ago. Fans were asked to come in for a fake
Cricket Wireless commercial audition only to be surprised by an unexpected
Cena in real life.
All I can think of when I see this clip is that game Bloody Mary or Beetlejuice.
Beetlejuice. It's showtime.
For more stories like these go to whatstrending.com, LIKE
and SUBSCRIBE for more.
